						<div class="postbody">I don't really think you need anything more than trigonometry for simple 2D games? If you don't have one already, make a sine/cosine table because it's essential for some more complicated (but still relevant) problems.<br /><br />Now, with 3D graphics, it's probably a whole other story...</div>

