				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Velocity is the integral of acceleration, and displacement is the integral of velocity. That's calculus. And when acceleration depends on some other variable, that's differential equations.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
						<tr valign="middle">
